GNDEC College Mess Management System


Project Idea Selection
Objective: Finalize project topic and understand problem domain
Activities:

Conducted preliminary research on college mess management challenges

Identified pain points: manual meal tracking, billing errors, time-consuming processes

Analyzed existing systems in GNDEC campus

Finalized "GNDEC College Mess Management System" as project title

Documented initial project scope and objectives

Key Decisions:

Digital solution to replace manual registers

Focus on accuracy in billing and meal tracking

Web-based system for accessibility
